    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事情节</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无血统，无姓名，代号ZY131385，欢迎进入《女神氪金系统》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不是想要逃离这个世界吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这就是机会，她们三人都是候选人，每一个都代表独一无二的世界体系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1号世界——校园女神，温柔甜美，青梅竹马：金梦</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/0c7756d380a77517f65f4a9fbe4e5016.poster.avif?t=1745702890\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/0c7756d380a77517f65f4a9fbe4e5016.webm?t=1745702890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/0c7756d380a77517f65f4a9fbe4e5016.mp4?t=1745702890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             金梦：哥哥，我们可以永远在一起吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2号世界——活泼可爱，古灵精怪，同居室友：木晴晴</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/b25befc6d9245f3bd580f045c65471d9.poster.avif?t=1745702890\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/b25befc6d9245f3bd580f045c65471d9.webm?t=1745702890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/b25befc6d9245f3bd580f045c65471d9.mp4?t=1745702890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             木晴晴：啊啊啊~大色狼！！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3号世界——成熟性感，泼辣冰山，霸道上司：水伊涵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/b13db31be52d436740f35474f23d3223.poster.avif?t=1745702890\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/b13db31be52d436740f35474f23d3223.webm?t=1745702890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332640/extras/b13db31be52d436740f35474f23d3223.mp4?t=1745702890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              水伊涵：遇到你，我不后悔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以随便选择一人，体验的新生活，留在新世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传统选项：玩家将在剧情中遇到各种简单又不简单的选择，这些选择会有不同的情节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日程安排：想要穿越到女神们的世界，与女神们展开一段专属约会，需要在每天安排日常，提升自己的属性和女神们的好感度，直到女神向你告白。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女神氪金系统：本作的一大特色，玩家在游戏中会获得积分，使用积分可以在系统中兑换氪金道具，正确的道具可以继续推进剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于我们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小伙伴们，好久不见！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是《女神保卫战》的制作组，这是我们尝试的第二部互动影视作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在经历了第一部纯粹的恋爱作品后，我们决定做一款不太一样的特殊的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作刻意以复古的vlog形式进行拍摄，让玩家体验最纯粹的日系约会养成游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢小伙伴们一直以来的大力支持，以及众筹大佬们的氪金支持！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们会继续努力，未来做出更多不同体验的互动影视作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么让我们进入《女神氪金系统》吧！</p>",
